data.description: Located just 1 mile from the University of Central Florida and Downtown Oviedo with "A" rated schools!! This ranch style home sits on a 1/3 acre lot, is of block construction and just had a new roof put on in 2018! Many upgrades have been done, including new gutters, a new circuit breaker box, new paver pool deck and new screen enclosures on the front porch and the pool! The floor plan is old Florida with lots of windows and a quaint wood burning fireplace! The kitchen overlooks the pool and has painted cabinets, granite and a cute backsplash. The family room is enormous and could be used for a TV room or even a home based business since there's a private door to the carport! The backyard is fully fenced with 6ft PVC and has 2 double gates allowing you to park vehicles, boats and even set up your workshop! There's even a 50amp RV hook up! The pool is a gorgeous dark aqua color and is larger than most! An open patio has a built in bench and would be a great spot for your pergola and the covered lanai has plenty of room to add a Summer kitchen! Enjoy no rear neighbors, no HOA, and live the way you want! There are plenty of places to eat and shop within a few miles and the NEW Oviedo Medical ER is just 3.5 miles away! Need more space? There's still plenty of room to add on and even build a garage!
